evidence_excerpts.text:
So the next human entered has his self at his space-time + Firebright who is me who is Thomas. I am to him or her (living later on) as Thomas is to me: a "rider".

{illustration of a triangle with an eye in it, and the text "Ajna" with an arrow pointing towards the eye}

So Thomas got into me originally as a Firebright - entered at some time early in my life. This is a secret of the true Xtians. Long ago I figured out most of this, how Christ passed on to those at Pentecost; Christ was the first
